data.description: Welcome to this charming home brimming w/character & timeless appeal in Colonial Place. Enter thru quaint front porch and prepare to be impressed. Gorgeous hardwoods throughout, beautiful doors & built-in features, every detail exudes warmth & charm. Two kitchens equipped w/stainless steel appliances, lovely tiled backsplashes, beautiful cabinetry & gas cooking—a perfect setup! One kitchen features a double-sided wood-burning fireplace that is open to the spacious family room which features an entire wall of beautifully designed stacked stone wall. The lighting throughout home adds to the charm of the old world feel. Beautifully updated luxurious bathrooms add a touch of modern elegance. Private yard features an amazing built in smoker! Many upgrades, including replaced electrical, windows & slate roof, ensuring both functionality & aesthetic appeal for years to come. Private side entrance to upstairs, detached garage, there is so much to experience - come & see first hand!
